Music executive and manager of award-winning singer, Wizkid has opened up on their relationship. Jada, who shares a son with the 31-year-old “Essence” global hit maker, said she loves the singer in a manner she’s never done anyone before. Pollock revealed this in an interactive session she hosted on her verified Twitter page on Friday, where a fan quizzed her to know if she loved Biz Wiz.   Everything about Genevieve is lovable, worth emulation…     Unfulfilled plans of late Dayo Kujore     I’m doing all that makes me happy in 2022 –…   The fan simply identified as ‘phillippop’ asked: “Do you love Big Wiz?” - Advertisement - The mother of one answered in the affirmative. She described their love as magical, noting she loves Stay boy with all her heart. “With all my heart! I have never loved anyone like this in my lifetime. Our love is magical”, Pollock tweeted.